author: @kendallcurtis7863
text:
This isn't AT ALL her independent revelation. It isn't a "revelation" at all. It is simple, self-interested greed's survival.¬†

She might as well be saying "I don't care about causes as much as I care about my pocket book". Hollywood as a whole has realized that they will lose to new competitors if they keep appealing to only one audience. It's why budgets and big-name actors are going to traditionally conservative friendly subject matter like ranching and living in middle America. It's why Nate Bargatze has hosted SNL twice in just a few years despite the entire staff hating conservatives. This is the "revelation" the studios have made after the 50th woke flop. So it took a LOT to get them there. 

Jennifer Lawrence is simply an opportunist like Emma Watson. She just sells the same idea better than Emma Watson. Secretly they still feel everything they always felt, which is superior and condescending. They simply now realize they can't win this superiority/enlightenment game (in their own heads anyway) and also stay rich. Simple as that.
